lead_paragraph: Cricket Australia will pore over its high performance systems in a 'meaty' review following the 3-0 test series whitewash to Sri Lanka, chief executive James Sutherland has said.

headline.print_headline: Australia to Conduct 'Meaty' Review After Sri Lanka Flop
